Тест 1:
Входные данные:
orders = [
    {"id": 101, "amount": 250, "currency": "USD"},
    {"id": 102, "amount": 400, "currency": "EUR"}
]

export_orders('orders1.xml', orders)

with open('orders1.xml', 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:
    print(f.read())

Ожидаемый вывод:
<orders>
  <order id="101">
    <amount>250</amount>
    <currency>USD</currency>
  </order>
  <order id="102">
    <amount>400</amount>
    <currency>EUR</currency>
  </order>
</orders>

